    "17": {
      "id": "17",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*The Crown of Karsus... You've read of such an artefact, but always in veiled terms, couched in myth and rumour. Never as a reality.*",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "23",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "20": {
          "id": "20",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*Could this truly be the crown you saw on the brain, surging with corrupted Netherese magic? If it is indeed Karsus' fabled creation, what else could it be capable of?*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "23",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "26": {
              "id": "26",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "A familiar feeling rises within you. Temptation...",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "23",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "13": {
                  "id": "13",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*This could be the answer to your prayers. A gift unlike any your goddess has been willing to give.*",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "12": {
                      "id": "12",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Reforge it, and you would carry the most powerful artefact in the realms. A better fate than the one Mystra offered you.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [
                        "ORI_Gale_Knows_ReadKarsusNotes"
                      ],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "27": {
                          "id": "27",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*She's aware of your discoveries - Elminster's visit betrays that much. What else does she know? What else hasn't she told you?*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "ORI_Gale_State_Met_ElminsterInWYR"
                          ],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "22": {
                              "id": "22",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*Between the Heavens and the Hells, the fate of the Crown hangs in the balance, and you will be the one to decide it.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [
                                "LOW_HouseOfHope_State_ContractIsDestroyed = False",
                                "GLO_Monitor_State_MadeDeal"
                              ],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            },
                            "15": {
                              "id": "15",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*It's time you sought out her shrine. There, she will acknowledge the secrets she's kept from you. And this time, she will not deny you anything.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "19": {
                          "id": "19",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*It's time the Mother of All Magic heard what you have to say. Time for you to find her shrine, and claim a long-witheld audience.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "ORI_Gale_State_Met_ElminsterInWYR = False"
                          ],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "14": {
                              "id": "14",
                              "speaker": "",
                              "text": "",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "22",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "jump",
                              "children": {}
                            },
                            "6": {
                              "id": "6",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*Whatever secrets Mystra keeps from you, she will surrender them. She has no choice, now the Crown of Karsus is almost within your reach.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "23": {
                      "id": "23",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*The orb, the parasite, and now the Crown... Netherese magic haunts you at every turn. It's time you understood its full potential.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "18": {
                          "id": "18",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*Sorcerous Sundries must be your next port of call.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [
                            "ORI_Gale_State_SentToFindBook"
                          ],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "2": {
                              "id": "2",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*If there is more to discover about Karsus' creations, their shelves are your best hope of finding it. And once you've learned his secrets, your prayers may finally be answered.*",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Sense of anticipation here at what this knowledge could give Gale",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "0": {
              "id": "0",
              "speaker": "Gale",
              "text": "Such power leads to only one outcome. Corruption...",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "23",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "3": {
                  "id": "3",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*In taking control of the Crown, the Dead Three's Chosen enslaved an elder brain, infecting half the Sword Coast with tadpoles. And that was without a true understanding of Karsus' powers.*",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "11": {
                      "id": "11",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Destroy the crown without first destroying your contract with Raphael, and there will be hells to pay. The devil will make sure of that.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [
                        "LOW_HouseOfHope_State_ContractIsDestroyed = False",
                        "GLO_Monitor_State_MadeDeal"
                      ],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
