              "children": {
                "9": {
                  "id": "9",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*Whatever the Crown's potential, for now it is impossible to detach from its wearer. So long as the elder brain lives, Karsus' Crown will never be yours.*",
                  "context": "",
